    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《领航员计划》是一款有美少女养成互动要素的弹幕射击肉鸽游戏，Roguelike刷宝玩法，数百种BUFF、武器、舰船、技能自由搭配！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/406da5bf0ffb8df73eba505bd34c7e89.poster.avif?t=1768121898\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/406da5bf0ffb8df73eba505bd34c7e89.webm?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/406da5bf0ffb8df73eba505bd34c7e89.mp4?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在星际探险中邂逅“领航员”，打造专属飞船，穿梭于异星战场，激战风格各异的敌舰。你将在名为“大洪水”的宇宙浩劫到来之际，探寻危机背后的秘密，突破重重难关，奔赴安全星域。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/98625209522f54f53d525e2f9e8494bd.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/98625209522f54f53d525e2f9e8494bd.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=126 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/aa1221ba6fa263de8b34172ef220c597.poster.avif?t=1768121898\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/aa1221ba6fa263de8b34172ef220c597.webm?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/aa1221ba6fa263de8b34172ef220c597.mp4?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用双摇杆操控，俯视角弹幕射击的游玩方式，结合Roguelike刷宝玩法，数百种BUFF、武器和特殊技能自由搭配，同时支持四人联机游玩。玩家通过养成各个种族的“领航员”角色，提升技能，解锁数十种Live2D动态立绘与互动剧情。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/eb666c3b565fc2d9095aeec3b60a6cb8.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/eb666c3b565fc2d9095aeec3b60a6cb8.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=126 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/858a06c434efa5b9bd4282db9ea25034.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/858a06c434efa5b9bd4282db9ea25034.avif?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=730 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中随机掉落各类强力武器，拾取并武装上阵！机枪、孢子炮、照射炮等，多样化的随机资源为每局战斗注入新鲜策略——用趁手的装备撕开敌群防线，让每一次突围都充满未知惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/820f287c30b8635c273334c8601e59ae.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/820f287c30b8635c273334c8601e59ae.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=126 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/f3069545ee6f6280b5c5beeaf99809d3.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/f3069545ee6f6280b5c5beeaf99809d3.avif?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当“大洪水”灾变席卷宇宙，你作为飞船驾驶员，将与领航员携手对抗未知种族的狂袭。在随机生成的星图关卡中探索资源、升级战舰，从危机四伏的宇宙战场突围——每一次突破都是向终点的靠近，安全星域正等待你们共同抵达。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/ab34d586ca9c6932c6e57ecc68ce39da.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/ab34d586ca9c6932c6e57ecc68ce39da.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=126 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/42488bac2881d36ba2aff09371d1a886.poster.avif?t=1768121898\" width=1170 height=1486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/42488bac2881d36ba2aff09371d1a886.webm?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/42488bac2881d36ba2aff09371d1a886.mp4?t=1768121898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/16a51f9fa8de749c60da9074f0546a06.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/16a51f9fa8de749c60da9074f0546a06.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=1925 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/407d6915af320c6ab3abe4cb19afac48.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/407d6915af320c6ab3abe4cb19afac48.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=1927 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras/2613d0d047b9d04d24290ce42c070d8c.avif?t=1768121898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123420/extras_big/2613d0d047b9d04d24290ce42c070d8c.webp?t=1768121898 width=1560 height=2015 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自高纬度文明的领航员拥有鲜明个性，你可以在三种进化路线中自由选择成长方向。随着领航员的成长，你将在战斗中和她并肩破局，同时在战斗外感受心动、建立羁绊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
